<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/22826103-capital-dames"><img alt="Capital Dames: the Civil War and the Women of Washington, 1848-1868" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1416178247l/22826103._SX98_.jpg" />
