      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/19683.Karen_Abbott">About Karen Abbott</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/19683.Karen_Abbott"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1558629949p3/19683.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/19683.Karen_Abbott">Karen Abbott
</a></div>
<div class='goodreadsAuthorBadge'></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
579
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer1551859559897197301">Karen Abbott is the New York Times bestselling author of <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/219780._Sin_in_the_Second_City__Madams__Ministers__Playboys__and_the_Battle_for_America_s_Soul' title=' Sin in the Second City: Madams, Ministers, Playboys, and the Battle for America&apos;s Soul' rel='nofollow noopener'> Sin in the Second City: Madams, Ministers, Playboys, and the Battle for America&apos;s Soul</a>, <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/8201605._American_Rose__A_Nation_Laid_Bare__The_Life_and_Times_of_Gypsy_Rose_Lee' title=' American Rose: A Nation Laid Bare: The Life and Times of Gypsy Rose Lee' rel='nofollow noopener'> American Rose: A Nation Laid Bare: The Life and Times of Gypsy Rose Lee</a>, <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18679391._Liar__Temptress__Soldier__Spy__Four_Women_Undercover_in_the_Civil_War' title=' Liar, Temptress, Soldier, Spy: Four Women Undercover in the Civil War' rel='nofollow noopener'> Liar, Temptress, Soldier, Spy: Four Women Undercover in the Civil War</a>, and, most recently, <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/43747492._The_Ghosts_of_Eden_Park__The_Bootleg_King__the_Women_Who_Pursued_Him__and_the_Murder_That_Shocked_Jazz__Age_America' title=' The Ghosts of Eden Park: The Bootleg King, the Women Who Pursued Him, and the Murder That Shocked Jazz- Age America' rel='nofollow noopener'> The Ghosts of Eden Park: The Bootleg King, the Women Who Pursued Him, and the Murder Th</a></span>
  <span id="freeText1551859559897197301" style="display:none">Karen Abbott is the New York Times bestselling author of <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/219780._Sin_in_the_Second_City__Madams__Ministers__Playboys__and_the_Battle_for_America_s_Soul" title=" Sin in the Second City: Madams, Ministers, Playboys, and the Battle for America's Soul" rel="nofollow noopener"> Sin in the Second City: Madams, Ministers, Playboys, and the Battle for America's Soul</a>, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/8201605._American_Rose__A_Nation_Laid_Bare__The_Life_and_Times_of_Gypsy_Rose_Lee" title=" American Rose: A Nation Laid Bare: The Life and Times of Gypsy Rose Lee" rel="nofollow noopener"> American Rose: A Nation Laid Bare: The Life and Times of Gypsy Rose Lee</a>, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18679391._Liar__Temptress__Soldier__Spy__Four_Women_Undercover_in_the_Civil_War" title=" Liar, Temptress, Soldier, Spy: Four Women Undercover in the Civil War" rel="nofollow noopener"> Liar, Temptress, Soldier, Spy: Four Women Undercover in the Civil War</a>, and, most recently, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/43747492._The_Ghosts_of_Eden_Park__The_Bootleg_King__the_Women_Who_Pursued_Him__and_the_Murder_That_Shocked_Jazz__Age_America" title=" The Ghosts of Eden Park: The Bootleg King, the Women Who Pursued Him, and the Murder That Shocked Jazz- Age America" rel="nofollow noopener"> The Ghosts of Eden Park: The Bootleg King, the Women Who Pursued Him, and the Murder That Shocked Jazz- Age America</a>, named an Amazon best book of the month for August 2019. She has written for newyorker.com, the Wall Street Journal, the Washington Post, Smithsonian Magazine, Salon and other publications.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1551859559897197301" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

